<s docid="AP890425-0013" num="40" wdcount="9"> ``God gave birth to 500 heroes,'' the captain said.</s>
<s docid="AP890425-0013" num="41" wdcount="10"> ``Fire on a ship is the most terrifying fear ...</s>
