<s docid="AP890425-0013" num="56" wdcount="15"> ``I'll be in the turret for the first shot to go off,'' the captain said.</s>
<s docid="AP890425-0013" num="57" wdcount="38"> One of the survivors, Gunner's Mate 3rd Class Kendall L. Truitt, 21, of Tampa, Fla., said that at first the men down in the powder magazine in the lowest level of the turret didn't know anything was wrong.</s>
